# Shared Styles Only

- Do not add inline `<style>` blocks in generated/static pages.
- Put reusable styles in:
  - `styles/site.css` (base, post pages, blog/tag lists),
  - `styles/site-components.css` (header + JS-hydrated components).
- For visual updates, change shared CSS first, not per-page HTML.
- Preserve class contracts used by JS hydration:
  - `post-list`, `post-card`, `post-card-title`, `post-card-desc`,
  - `post-nav post-nav-related`, `blog-card`, `blog-card-title`, `blog-card-desc`.
- Keep colors in the existing palette (`--bg`, `--ink`, `--ink-soft`, `--accent`, `--line`).
